author: Reuters Editorial
title: Largest supermoon of 2020 rises on a world battling COVID-19
description: The largest, brightest supermoon of 2020 rose in the night sky on Tuesday over hushed cities, stilled factories and countries in lockdown due to the novel coronavirus that has killed tens of thousands worldwide.
